ly.\nWhen we balance the core criteria\u2014reliability, technical and cognitive competence, calm judgment under pressure, and the ability to work safely with a crew\u2014Candidate\u202fD offers the strongest overall fit. His reliability and problem\u2011solving strengths outweigh the relatively milder, less\u2011specific interpersonal concerns, especially compared with the clear teamwork deficits of Candidates\u202fB and\u202fC and the ambiguous but potentially problematic traits of Candidate\u202fA.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fD\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate D\"}"}
